# OPTIONAL — only needed if the pinned trial package has expired and fails to render.
#
# This repo depends on the trial build of Scheduler Pro by default
# (see package.json: "npm:@bryntum/schedulerpro-trial@7.3.1"). Trial builds carry a
# runtime expiration date. If the scheduler refuses to render, switch to your own
# licensed registry access:
#
#   1. Copy this file to `.npmrc` (which is gitignored — never commit a token).
#   2. Fill in your Bryntum registry token below.
#   3. In package.json, change the "@bryntum/schedulerpro" dependency from
#      "npm:@bryntum/schedulerpro-trial@7.3.1" to "7.3.1" (the licensed build).
#   4. Re-run `npm install`.
#
# Use YOUR OWN Bryntum registry credentials.

@bryntum:registry=https://npm.bryntum.com
//npm.bryntum.com/:_authToken=YOUR_BRYNTUM_REGISTRY_TOKEN
